title: Series of Unfortunate Events (iPod format)
description:
This is a collection of all 13 Lemony Snicket audiobooks along with the soundtracks from each book. The audiobooks are formatted for iPods and iTunes and will show up under the audiobooks menu. They will remember your position if you stop and listen to something else and will not be affected by shuffle.

audiobooks were assembled using ssa - http://www.jrlearnsmedia.com/blog
